headline: Costco follows Walmart, a weight loss drug panic, and an airline's hotel fail: Business news roundup
summary: Costco is reportedly demanding price cuts from its Chinese suppliers as U.S. tariffs continue to take a toll.

headline: Future of retail: Key trends and potential winners
summary: Investing.com -- The future of retail over the next decade will be shaped by continued e-commerce growth, rising retail media, geopolitical shifts, and evolving consumer behavior, Bernstein said in a note.
